OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777993872
OL,3,CCars crash into homes on Tyneside
OL,4,Ccausing damage
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after
OL,7,Fvehicles crashed into two properties
OL,8,Fon Tyneside.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police is investigating
OL,11,Ftwo separate incidents - one in
OL,12,FNewcastle and another Gateshead -
OL,13,Fwhich are not currently being linked.
OL,15,FThe force said an incident in the
OL,16,FThrockley area of Newcastle saw a
OL,17,Fvehicle reverse into a property just
OL,18,Fbefore 11:45pm on Monday (4 May).
OL,20,FThe occupants reportedly fled the area
OL,21,Fand no one was injured.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
