OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777993872
OL,3,CCars crash into homes on Tyneside
OL,4,Ccausing damage
OL,6,FA Northumbria Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Just before 11.45pm yesterday
OL,8,F(Monday), we received a report of a
OL,9,Fdisturbance in the Throckley area.
OL,11,F"It was reported that, for reasons yet
OL,12,Fto be established, a vehicle had
OL,13,Freversed into a property on The
OL,14,FCrescent. The vehicle and its
OL,15,Foccupants were then reported to have
OL,16,Fmade off from the scene.
OL,18,F"Emergency services attended, with no
OL,19,Finjuries reported. An investigation
OL,20,Fhas been launched and enquires are
OL,21,Fongoing to locate those responsible."
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOU
