OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777993872
OL,3,CCars crash into homes on Tyneside
OL,4,Ccausing damage
OL,6,FJust over one hour later a car crashed
OL,7,Finto a home in Gateshead causing
OL,8,Fstructural damage.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police said the incident
OL,11,Fin Balmlaw, in the Beacon Lough area,
OL,12,Fhappened at about 12:50am on Tuesday
OL,13,F(5 May).
OL,15,FThe force said no serious injuries
OL,16,Fwere caused and the occupants of the
OL,17,Fvehicle fled the scene before officers
OL,18,Farrived.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
