CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777993872
OL,3,CCars crash into homes on Tyneside
OL,4,Ccausing damage
OL,6,FThe area has been taped off by police
OL,7,Fthroughout the morning, with the
OL,8,Fvehicle involved having since been
OL,9,Fremoved from the scene.
OL,11,FA Northumbria Police spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "At around 12.50am today
OL,13,F(Tuesday), we received a report of a
OL,14,Fcollision on Balmlaw in the Beacon
OL,15,FLough area of Gateshead.
OL,17,F"Emergency services attended where a
OL,18,Fvehicle had collided with the front of
OL,19,Fa residential property, causing
OL,20,Fstructural damage.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
