FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777993872
OL,3,CCars crash into homes on Tyneside
OL,4,Ccausing damage
OL,6,F"The occupants from the vehicle had
OL,7,Ffled the area before police arrival.
OL,8,FThankfully no serious injuries were
OL,9,Freported, however those in the address
OL,10,Fwere left shaken as a result.
OL,12,F"An investigation has been launched to
OL,13,Festablish the full circumstances and
OL,14,Flocate those involved. Officers remain
OL,15,Fin the area to carry out enquiries and
OL,16,Foffer reassurance to the wider
OL,17,Fcommunity."
OL,19,FAnyone with information about either
OL,20,Fincident should contact the force on
OL,21,F101.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
